metadata.name: Crystal Frogs FF #1
metadata.description: Crystal Frog #1 is a prestigious member of the Founding Frogs, the elite group of pioneers who embarked on the thrilling journey of the Crystal Frogs animated series. As a Founding Frog holder, you have exclusive access to our pitch deck development, VIP events, and higher yield of crystals through our staking platform. Join us in shaping the destiny of this groundbreaking community-driven cartoon series. Ribbit!
